        "TileImage": "$($repository cea45903-4e6b-425f-b27a-00200971d2bc).Image",
        "Description": "Sierra Knox is very talented. She&apos;s also very bad at winning races when Moses Lee is in them. Rather than suggest she practice more, the Knox family has gone with Plan B: hire a professional. While you&apos;re down there, Sheikh Salman Al-Shammari has been squeezing the Knoxes on a sponsorship deal and frankly nobody likes him either. Two birds, one very bald man in a suit. Don&apos;t let either of them see the podium.",
